28
00:01:00,740 --> 00:01:03,800
Get ready for that, because it’s already
underway.

29
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:04,800
In Europe,

30
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:07,630
Chinese companies have bought stakes in 13
ports—

31
00:01:07,630 --> 00:01:09,680
all within the past decade.

32
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:11,430
And as of 2019,

33
00:01:11,430 --> 00:01:13,320
Chinese state-controlled companies are handling

34
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:17,310
10 percent of Europe’s shipping container
traffic.

35
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:19,080
Why isn’t this big news?

36
00:01:19,080 --> 00:01:21,070
Because—let’s be honest,

37
00:01:21,070 --> 00:01:23,430
