54
00:01:58,740 --> 00:02:01,440
The port of Zeebrugge, in Bruges, Belgium.

55
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:03,290
Not super exciting, I know.

56
00:02:03,290 --> 00:02:04,490
And that’s why very few people

57
00:02:04,490 --> 00:02:05,920
