79
00:02:56,070 --> 00:02:57,630
Just a year and a half later—

80
00:02:57,630 --> 00:03:00,240
that’s fast in European Union time—

81
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,620
the EU council approved a new set of rules

82
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:04,800
